{"tid":880794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IBM 330億美元買下Red Hat 成立107年來最大手筆併購","createTime":"2018-10-29T03:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T03:15:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8dc45da0e418c52a8e606914cc7e5e7189ea9e","tid":880794,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"IBM以340億美元併購雲端軟體業者Red Hat，有意藉此歷來最大併購在雲端領域迎頭趕上。<br />\n<br />\nIBM將以每股190美元現金併購Red Hat，較Red Hat上周五收盤溢價63%。<br />\n<br />\nIBM董事長暨執行長羅梅娣發布新聞稿說：「併購Red Hat將突破局面，改變雲端市場的一切。」羅梅娣正努力帶領107年歷史的IBM轉向更現代化的事業，像是雲端、人工智慧和資安軟體。<br />\n<br />\n併購Red Hat後，IBM可立即挹注雲端事業營收，也將原本透過IBM在全球銷售部門代銷的軟體產品納歸自己旗下。<br />\n<br />\nRed Hat以自己的Linux作業系統為基礎銷售軟體和服務，拜Red Hat Enterprise Linux產品吸引大客戶所賜，今年營收可望首度突破30億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/29/realtime/5457181.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2Frealtime%2F5457181.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=358c12b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIBM要藉歷來最大併購一口氣在雲端領域急起直追。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3448114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3448114&d=a6A4ND9xobPGM80ooQRdy8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a39f1aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3448114</a>"}]}